<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 26 日星期五 17:17:11 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[US Presidential Race: Will DeSantis Sink Like Atlantis After Glitchy Twitter Launch?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110606304" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110560605_0:0:2698:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_3df4eca9b7a6f60814cd046a118f41ff.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1110560587" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/us-presidential-race-will-desantis-sink-like-atlantis-after-glitchy-twitter-launch-1110606304.html?share-img=1110560587"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / KIMIMASA MAYAMA</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2023 年 4 月 24 日，佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯（右）在其妻子凯西（左）与日本首相岸田文雄在东京官邸会面后向记者挥手致意</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="Florida Governor Ron DeSantis (R) waves to journalists as his wife Casey (L) looks one after meeting Japanese Prime Minister Fumio Kishida at the latter's official residence in Tokyo on April 24, 2023 - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="2023 年 4 月 24 日，佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯（右）在与日本首相岸田文雄在东京官邸会面后向记者挥手致意，他的妻子凯西（左）看起来像" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110560605_0:265:2698:1783_1920x0_80_0_0_ca00421306064812d2bbe6598e2e77e1.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110560605_0:265:2698:1783_640x0_80_0_0_6de3399cfb0b3059b78da4e5485d385e.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110560605_0:265:2698:1783_1280x0_80_0_0_3f48c7f346bef02fdb5747ecca797b49.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/18/1110560605_0:265:2698:1783_1920x0_80_0_0_ca00421306064812d2bbe6598e2e77e1.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©<a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">法新社 2023</a> / KIMIMASA MAYAMA </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="James Tweedie - Sputnik International" title="詹姆斯·特威迪" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/08/1c/1080307270_0:3:397:400_100x100_80_0_0_7777393b9b18802f2e3c5eaa9cbcc612.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">詹姆斯·特威迪</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tweedie_james/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:j.tweedie@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">Ready For Ron 政治行动委员会执行主任加布里埃尔·兰内斯 (Gabriel Llanes) 表示，在特朗普试图重新争取 2020 年大选的同时，佛罗里达州州长向选民提供了一个“未来”。克莱姆森大学政治学家大卫伍德德教授​​说他的推特活动是最新的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 总统竞选的竞选经理相信他可以攀登唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的民调领先优势。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周三，佛罗里达州州长通过 Twitter 网络广播<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/florida-governor-ron-desantis-announces-2024-presidential-election-campaign-1110571472.html" target="_blank">宣布</a>参选共和党初选。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他已经成为前总统唐纳德特朗普的第二大竞争对手，超越了特朗普的副总统迈克彭斯和前联合国大使妮基黑莉。但南卡罗来纳州参议员蒂姆斯科特的参选可能会改变这一点。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">共和党初选的获胜者可能会在 2024 年大选中与总统乔·拜登对决。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>加布里埃尔·兰内斯</strong><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/ron-desantis-announces-bid-for-presidency-surprise-1110588608.html" target="_blank">告诉</a>人造卫星网，佛罗里达州州长竞选公告中广受嘲笑的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/twitter-engineering-chief-leaves-the-nest-after-ron-desantis-glitchy-presidential-launch-1110598114.html" target="_blank">技术问题</a>实际上是他获得民众支持的标志。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “你有 500,000 人试图挤进服务器，服务器，每 30 秒就有 50,000 人尝试登录，”他说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110606304" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/us-presidential-race-will-desantis-sink-like-atlantis-after-glitchy-twitter-launch-1110606304.html?share-block=1110611282" data-title="&quot;You had 500,000 people trying to cram on to the server, to the server, and it was an additional 50,000 attempting every 30 seconds to log on,&quot; he said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">特朗普在最近的共和党选民民调中以超过 50% 的支持率以压倒性优势领先，而德桑蒂斯充其量只能在 20 多岁左右萎靡不振。但竞选组织者认为这是大牌候选人的早期激增。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我不太关注民意调查。如今的民意调查方法并不是非常可靠，”兰内斯坚持说。 “我会提醒人们，距离选举还有 75 周，罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 的支持率已经达到 20%，这意味着四分之一的初选选民已经决定他们喜欢罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis)，而他甚至还没有宣布。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他指出，在 2008 年第一次民主党初选之前，当时的参议员巴拉克奥巴马远远落后于希拉里克林顿。 “我向你保证，投票将在未来……两三个月内开始结束。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> PAC 主任表示，与 2008 年和 2016 年一样，选民希望领导层真正发生变化——小罗伯特·肯尼迪在民主党初选中对拜登的左翼挑战就证明了这一点</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “就像 RFK 这样的人开始在民主党方面获得如此好的民意调查一样，人们只是想要改变，他们想要新的东西。”兰内斯说，并指出特朗普仍在抱怨 2020 年大选中的选票舞弊。 “他不会停止谈论它令人作呕。我相信这是他最大的失败。他没有给我们未来。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110606304" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/us-presidential-race-will-desantis-sink-like-atlantis-after-glitchy-twitter-launch-1110606304.html?share-block=1110611182" data-title="&amp;quot;The same reason why you have somebody like RFK is starting to poll so well on the Democratic side, people just want a change, they want something new.&amp;quot; Llanes said, pointing out that Trump was still complaining of ballot fraud in the 2020 election. &amp;quot;He won&amp;#x27;t stop talking about it nauseum. I do believe that is his biggest downfall. He doesn&amp;#x27;t give us a future.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>大卫伍德德教授</strong>​​告诉人造卫星，他对科技大亨埃隆马斯克在他最近收购的社交媒体网站上主持德桑蒂斯竞选活动并不感到惊讶。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “使用 Twitter 是因为它是下一个通信媒体，将取代电视和其他主流媒体，”他说。 “这对德桑蒂斯来说不是一个很好的发布，但他正在努力推动优势，这将在未来帮助他。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">但这位学者表示，拥有 Twitter 不会让马斯克成为政治“造王者”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">伍德沃德说：“事实是，美国选民不会被任何一件事左右，无论是外表、金钱还是地位。” “选民珍视他们的独立性，并且在被受欢迎的人物使用时善变。出于多种原因，德桑蒂斯是一个强有力的候选人，我相信马斯克可以提供帮助，但是任何候选人都不应该在定义上接近任何一件事他自己。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110606304" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/us-presidential-race-will-desantis-sink-like-atlantis-after-glitchy-twitter-launch-1110606304.html?share-block=1110611364" data-title="&quot;The facts are that American voters are not swayed by any one thing, not looks, not money and not position,&quot; Woodward said. &quot;Voters treasure their independence and are fickle when it comes to being used by popular figures. DeSantis is a strong candidate for a number of reasons, and I'm sure Musk can help, however no candidate should get close to any one thing in defining himself.&quot;  "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位教授怀疑这位推特老板和特斯拉汽车公司的创始人是否像其他亿万富翁乔治索罗斯或查尔斯科赫那样有政治野心。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “如果马斯克将自己与任何一个政党或一个政治人物联系在一起，他就会失去很多，”伍德德争辩道。 “我认为他不会站在试图选举总统或控制政党的最前沿。在未来的某个时候，德桑蒂斯必须在一场正面交锋的选举中击败特朗普——那将是一个转折点。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他说，除了马斯克的支持，佛罗里达州州长挑战特朗普的共和党候选人资格，还有许多其他因素在起作用。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伍德沃德说：“他将需要很多支持，特朗普将不得不在他曾经强大的地方被击败，其他候选人将不得不退出。” “如果事情如他所愿，德桑蒂斯可以感谢马斯克。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong><em>如需对新闻事件进行更深入的评论，请关注我们的 Sputnik 电台节目<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/radio_fault_lines/" target="_blank">Fault Lines。</a></em></strong></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 16:23:16 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/us-presidential-race-will-desantis-sink-like-atlantis-after-glitchy-twitter-launch-1110606304.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/us-presidential-race-will-desantis-sink-like-atlantis-after-glitchy-twitter-launch-1110606304.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>罗恩德桑蒂斯</category><category>唐纳德·特朗普</category><category>埃隆·马斯克</category><category>共和党人</category><category>推特</category><category>佛罗里达</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>巴拉克奥巴马</category><category>希拉里·克林顿</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why is Russia Deploying Tactical Nuclear Weapons in Belarus?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110607130" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/05/04/1095255381_0:0:1496:1056_1440x900_80_0_1_ec74a8f687155dfd53d3c7e817b05249.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1095255377" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/why-is-russia-deploying-tactical-nuclear-weapons-in-belarus-1110607130.html?share-img=1095255377"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Russian Defence Ministry</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">伊斯坎德尔短程弹道导弹系统在俄罗斯在乌克兰的军事行动中使用</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt=" Iskander short-range ballistic missile system is used during the Russian military operation in Ukraine - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="俄罗斯在乌克兰的军事行动中使用伊斯坎德尔短程弹道导弹系统" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/05/04/1095255381_0:213:1496:1056_1920x0_80_0_0_73ad729725a0601f29d8034ad48c2486.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/05/04/1095255381_0:213:1496:1056_640x0_80_0_0_b48e1385fb56bdbb00b0be66c0d8bef8.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/05/04/1095255381_0:213:1496:1056_1280x0_80_0_0_b314ecfba4e2623bdb90365e841615cb.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/05/04/1095255381_0:213:1496:1056_1920x0_80_0_0_73ad729725a0601f29d8034ad48c2486.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / 俄罗斯国防部</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Oleg Burunov - Sputnik International" title="奥列格布鲁诺夫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/09/0b/1080424846_0:0:2048:2048_100x100_80_0_0_3d7b461f8a98586fa3fe739930816aea.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">奥列格布鲁诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_burunov_oleg/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:o.burunov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">俄罗斯和明斯克宣布本周签署一项关于在白俄罗斯领土上维持俄罗斯战术核武器的协议，重申这是对不友好国家奉行的侵略政策的回应。是什么促使莫斯科在白俄罗斯部署非战略核武器？人造卫星探索。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">什么是交易？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">本周早些时候，俄罗斯国防部长<em>谢尔盖绍伊古</em>和白俄罗斯国防部长<em>维克多赫列宁</em>在明斯克签署了一系列文件，以确定在白俄罗斯境内的一个特殊储存设施中维护俄罗斯<strong>非战略核武器的</strong>程序。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在此之前， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221229/putin-says-4-more-nuclear-powered-submarines-to-be-built-under-current-weapons-program-1105882697.html" target="_blank">俄罗斯总统普京</a>在 3 月下旬宣布，莫斯科和明斯克已同意在白俄罗斯部署俄罗斯的<strong>战术核武器</strong>，他强调此举不会违反俄罗斯关于不扩散核武器的承诺。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">不久之后，俄罗斯驻明斯克大使<em>鲍里斯·格雷兹洛夫</em>表示，战术核武器将部署在靠近白俄罗斯和俄罗斯联盟国西部边界的地方。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">什么是战术核武器？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">战术核武器 (TNW)，也称为<strong>非战略核武器</strong>(NSNW)，包括设计用于战场或有限打击的小型核弹头和运载系统。 TNW 包括重力炸弹、 <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230403/inside-the-iskander-a-closer-look-at-russias-deadly-short-range-missile-1109080044.html" target="_blank">短程导弹</a>、炮弹、地雷、深水炸弹和配备核弹头的鱼雷。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>与战略核武器相比，NSNW 的威力较小，旨在摧毁特定区域的敌方目标，而不会造成广泛的破坏和放射性尘埃。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> TNW 的当量从几分之一千吨到大约<em>50 千吨</em>不等，而战略核武器的当量从<em>100 千吨</em>到超过百万吨不等。重要的是，截至 2023 年，还没有在战斗情况下使用过任何战术核武器。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">莫斯科尚未公布其 TNW 数量或与武器相关的任何其他细节，但华盛顿辩称，俄罗斯与 TNW 相关的数字据称是美国的 10 倍。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">俄罗斯在白俄罗斯部署战术核武器的背后是什么？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">白俄罗斯外交部宣布本周莫斯科-明斯克签署关于在其近邻领土上维持俄罗斯 NSNW 的文件，重申这是对不友好国家奉行的侵略政策的回应。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该部得到了<em>谢尔盖绍伊古</em>的回应，他提到俄罗斯在白俄罗斯部署战术核武器时强调，由于“威胁急剧升级”，莫斯科和明斯克被迫就军事核领域的报复措施做出适当决定在两国的西部边界。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “我想指出，所有活动都是严格按照现有国际义务组织的，没有违反《不扩散核武器条约》，”绍伊古说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110607130" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/why-is-russia-deploying-tactical-nuclear-weapons-in-belarus-1110607130.html?share-block=1110610536" data-title="&quot;I would like to note that all the activities are organized strictly in accordance with existing international obligations and do not violate the Treaty on the Non-Proliferation of Nuclear Weapons,” Shoigu said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">克里姆林宫发言人德米特里佩斯科夫也同意这一观点，他告诉记者，莫斯科知道明斯克正面临邻国“非常不友好甚至敌对”的态度，包括“干涉白俄罗斯内政的意图”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>他说，所有这些都表明白俄罗斯和俄罗斯都面临着非常敌对的环境，这反过来又促使两国进一步加强伙伴关系，特别是在军事领域的双边关系方面。佩斯科夫没有具体说明俄罗斯是否已经开始在白俄罗斯部署 TNW。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 3 月下旬，明斯克明确表示，在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230408/where-are-us-nuclear-weapons-located-1109264542.html" target="_blank">美国及其盟国</a>施加多年压力以改变白俄罗斯的政治和地缘政治进程后，它决定接待俄罗斯 NSNW。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “在过去两年半的时间里，白俄罗斯共和国承受着来自美国、英国及其北约盟国以及欧盟成员国前所未有的政治、经济和信息压力。在鉴于这些情况，以及由此产生的国家安全领域的合理关切和风险，白俄罗斯被迫通过加强自身的安全和防御能力来做出回应，”白俄罗斯外交部在一份声明中说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110607130" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/why-is-russia-deploying-tactical-nuclear-weapons-in-belarus-1110607130.html?share-block=1110609909" data-title="&amp;quot;Over the last two and a half years, the Republic of Belarus has been subjected to unprecedented political, economic and information pressure from the United States, the United Kingdom and its NATO allies, as well as the member states of the European Union. In view of these circumstances, and the legitimate concerns and risks in the sphere of national security arising from them, Belarus is forced to respond by strengthening its own security and defense capabilities,&amp;quot; the Belarusian Foreign Ministry said in a statement."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">普京总统对俄罗斯在白俄罗斯土地上部署 TNW 有何看法？</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">普京总统在接受俄罗斯媒体采访时回忆说，白俄罗斯总统<em>卢卡申科</em>此前曾敦促莫斯科在白俄罗斯部署核武器。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>俄罗斯总统强调，在白俄罗斯<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230321/putin-russia-will-be-force-to-react-if-west-starts-using-weapons-with-nuclear-components-1108657136.html" target="_blank">部署 TNW 的直接导火索</a>是英国政府决定向乌克兰提供含有贫铀的穿甲弹，他说这“在某种程度上与核技术有关”。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110607130" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/why-is-russia-deploying-tactical-nuclear-weapons-in-belarus-1110607130.html?share-block=1110609910" data-title="The Russian president underlined that the immediate trigger for the deployment of TNWs in Belarus was the UK government’s decision to provide Ukraine with armor-piercing shells containing depleted uranium, something that he said was “one way or another related to nuclear technology.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">普京强调，通过在白俄罗斯部署 NSNW，俄罗斯将做美国几十年来所做的事情，将其战术核武器部署在比利时、德国、意大利、荷兰和土耳其。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据俄罗斯总统称，莫斯科已经帮助明斯克升级了 10 架白俄罗斯飞机，使其能够携带核武器。他说，俄罗斯还向白俄罗斯提供了可以配备常规弹头或核弹头的<strong><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221224/russian-s-400s-iskanders-sent-to-belarus-will-boost-joint-air-defense--foreign-ministry-1105746024.html" target="_blank">伊斯坎德尔短程导弹系统</a></strong>。普京补充说，白俄罗斯战术核武器储存设施的建设将于7月1日完成。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 15:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/why-is-russia-deploying-tactical-nuclear-weapons-in-belarus-1110607130.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/why-is-russia-deploying-tactical-nuclear-weapons-in-belarus-1110607130.html<category>人造卫星解释</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>白俄罗斯</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>亚历山大·卢卡申科</category><category>伊斯坎德尔弹道导弹</category><category>战术核武器</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Final Countdown: Goldman Sachs Economists Expect US Default by June 9]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110611592" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/09/1082297338_0:0:1920:1280_1440x900_80_0_1_82c4e569b1564e5f02a624e42ea8141d.jpg?source-sid=" data-photoview-image-id="1082297336" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/the-final-countdown-goldman-sachs-economists-expect-us-default-by-june-9-1110611592.html?share-img=1082297336"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Pixabay/CC0</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">时钟，夏令时，夏令时</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="" alt="Clock, Daylight Saving Time, DST  - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="时钟、夏令时、DST" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/09/1082297338_0:100:1921:1180_1920x0_80_0_0_331582321a4660b0deb091fc52f47560.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/09/1082297338_0:100:1921:1180_640x0_80_0_0_9bd956a0d318fc5bb03807642c61116a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/09/1082297338_0:100:1921:1180_1280x0_80_0_0_4df33ae3f9c22f231cbf00a1affd7919.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/09/1082297338_0:100:1921:1180_1920x0_80_0_0_331582321a4660b0deb091fc52f47560.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©Pixabay/CC0 </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">芳汀嘉迪尼耶</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_gardinier_fantine/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">为世界上最大的银行之一工作的两位经济学家宣布了一个惊人的消息：美国政府在被迫拖欠债务之前还剩下大约两周的钱。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">高盛 (Goldman Sachs) 的亚历克菲利普斯 (Alec Phillips) 和蒂姆克鲁帕 (Tim Krupa) 周五表示，根据他们的计算，到 6 月 2 日，美国将只剩下 300 亿美元来支付其先前的债务限额义务，并且该账户将在6 月 9 日。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>美国财政部给国会规定了 6 月 1 日的最后期限，在此之前达成协议以提高债务上限 - 这是一个自我强加的拨款限制，阻止立法者向联邦政府提供更多资金。 Phillips 和 Krupa 表示，截止日期“在我们看来非常准确”，因为它可能只留下一周的回旋余地。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">债务上限早在 1 月份就已达到，但现在控制美国众议院的共和党人拒绝延长上限，因为他们看到了违约威胁的机会，迫使民主党同意大幅削减预算，否则他们会反对.但由于民主党顽固地拒绝同意削减预算，而共和党人对预算限制作为债务上限法案的一部分毫不妥协，摊牌已经拖了几个月。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>财政部已采取“非常措施”在争端中继续支付账单， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/us-treasury-reportedly-asks-if-federal-agencies-can-delay-payments-to-avert-debt-default-1110546437.html" target="_blank">转移</a>已经拨付的资金以防止违约。但这些努力只能持续这么久，财政部长珍妮特耶伦警告说，国会预算办公室等其他预算专家证实了她的担忧。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">尽管如此， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/biden-mccarthy-near-debt-ceiling-deal-as-possible-default-looms-with-june-1-deadline-1110594657.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">谈判仍在继续</a>，美国总统乔拜登取消了亚洲之行以领导华盛顿的谈判。美国媒体周五报道称，拜登和众议院议长凯文麦卡锡 (R-CA) 即将达成协议，但几个关键问题仍悬而未决，包括缩减聘请更多国税局 (IRS) 审计员的计划，停止非国防可自由支配支出是否会超过 2023 年的水平，以及该协议是否会将债务上限提高一两年。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>高盛 (Goldman Sachs) 经济学家菲利普斯 (Phillips) 和克鲁帕 (Krupa) 给出了 80% 的可能性，即在周六之前达成一项全面的协议，10% 的可能性只是一项短期协议，以避免即将发生的违约。他们给出了 10% 的可能性，即国会不会及时采取行动，美国政府将拖欠债务。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">违约几乎肯定会破坏政府的信用评级并引发经济危机。 2011 年，类似的危机导致标准普尔和穆迪的债券评级公司将美国联邦政府的评级从 AAA 下调至 AA+，尽管技术上避免了违约，并且在违约发生前几个小时就达成了协议。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 15:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/the-final-countdown-goldman-sachs-economists-expect-us-default-by-june-9-1110611592.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/the-final-countdown-goldman-sachs-economists-expect-us-default-by-june-9-1110611592.html<category>美洲</category><category>高盛</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>默认</category></item></channel></rss>